3.  <span data-ttu-id="a09c2-111">使用 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElementCollection> 方法，按照前面介绍的顺序将已创建的元素添加到 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElementCollection.InsertItem%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a09c2-111">Add the created elements in the order described previously to the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElementCollection> using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingElementCollection.InsertItem%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
